summary: Adds a very special item called cinderwasp honey to skyrim. Worth a lot because it's useful and has monetary value.
descriptionHtml: Adds a very special item called Cinderwasp honey to skyrim. Worth a lot because it's useful and has monetary value. There's 15 all over skyrim and solsteim. Adds night-vision, heals 50 health and cures poison. Some are hidden well, others are not so much. If you collect them all you win a prize! I made this mostly for my friends, but I still appreciate feedback.
author: adrian85858
